response.overview: DDT Pro-Wrestling presented Wrestle Peter Pan 2025 – Night 2 on August 31, 2025, from Korakuen Hall in Tokyo, Japan. The second night of DDT’s biggest annual event featured championship bouts, faction clashes, and a special retirement road match for Hiroshi Tanahashi. Hiroshi Tanahashi continued his Retirement Road tour with a featured singles match against Danshoku Dieno. Kazusada Higuchi defended the KO-D Openweight Championship against Yuki Ueno. Minoru Suzuki put the DDT Universal Championship on the line against MAO
response.title: DDT Wrestle Peter Pan 2025 - Night 2
